abstract: >-
  Universal memory Skill and contextual memory protocol for LLM/SLM agents.
  CODEC-CORTEX organizes persistent agent memory as structured operational
  context through .cortex, provides HCORTEX for human audit and correction,
  and documents a planned deterministic codec/runtime/MCP automation path.
